### glibc
Important and most used lib the "GNU C Library"

###

> ldd /bin/cp   shows all needed libs
    *.so            shared lib
    .a              static
    .so.N           version

/lib /lib64 /usr/lib

### Runtime linker ld.so
/etc/ld.so.cach     for faster lib search
ldconfig            is started after restart
                    should be always used if manualy packets
                    are installed
